We are generating documentation with mike. You need to reference code directly, as in e.g. 

```
::: macromodel.agents.agent
    options:
        members:
            - Agent
```

this will directly take the docstrings from the code.

Every time you do this, you MUST CHECK the source.py file first to make sure everything is coherent. 